{"tid":339310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樓價準備跌，你們應當悔改","createTime":"2017-07-29T03:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T04:46:38.000Z","uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d8b96b7ed0ac122fd6b7790d43ff4f4c70a8829","tid":339310,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"留意返過去個十年私樓供應都係得每年萬幾，所以先有升無跌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果未來3年真係有10萬個供應，即係每年有成3萬幾，再加埋公屋每年一萬，有成4萬供應per year, 仲勁過港英年代嘅供應<br />\n<br />\n02，03年個兩年好似有成5萬供應per year(加埋公屋)<br />\n<br />\n照推斷，今次未必有03年跌得咁勁，但所造成嘅災難，特別係大量支那人而家入左市，仲有d咩3年唔準買賣嘅ssd，諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家寧願放d錢去買保險狗d咩美金收息plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f8b51ffe2c632d637bd33c76a9fc79a656e5e8","tid":339310,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:11:15.000Z","msg":"如果係4年10萬，每年得返2.5萬，其實就唔係話太多，但就一定止住升勢，到時大部分人問點解買樓無錢賺，我就拎住美金收息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db89799b3e00f238a35ad216ef6853e03d294170","tid":339310,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"佢其實應該等縮表推冧樓價先再推<br />\n自己推冧又八萬五翻版"},{"pid":"316e6a577943f85461f345828688238930972bd7","tid":339310,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"梗係買YEN啦<br />\n美金同英磅呢幾年都危危乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跌唔係問題<br />\n最驚啲人個個諗住趁低吸納<br />\n最後發現樓價以後都唔會大升<br />\n<br />\n好多香港人信經驗唔理經濟結構改變<br />\n97嗰陣經濟轉型就係個好例子"},{"pid":"8d61f95d18b6b9c53214f87bc4d8fae6a5efb449","tid":339310,"uid":105658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:48:27.000Z","msg":"樓主又係你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9b9946a68e7df7a23f1804e4d20647af5dd30c","tid":339310,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:50:29.000Z","msg":"我朋友06年買樓，啱啱供完層樓<br />\n宜家按左層樓去買元朗站上蓋，成五六百個"},{"pid":"e84d8f03830ec2d54df98799348dcceb02321722","tid":339310,"uid":59641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係4年10萬，每年得返2.5萬，其實就唔係話太多，但就一定止住升勢，到時大部分人問點解買樓無錢賺，我就拎住美金收息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用緊美金買緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d91878cc3decb59dd1f3070cb08e493c295f53","tid":339310,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:56:59.000Z","msg":"CCL 160 now"},{"pid":"965dbb5c3e30672f65f550ba53f5032813bc6425","tid":339310,"uid":110286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:59:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98e3f442f616b6411174637bd5bf66201de8ab24","tid":339310,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:02:55.000Z","msg":"叫左跌有冇十年？<br />\n零八年比你老師又中左一次，你有冇把握機會？<br />\n<br />\n信你咪好似你青城派個水晶姥姥咁賣左層樓買唔返囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432b233d5e4bbb2396867ad477dbc73da93081ee","tid":339310,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫左跌有冇十年？<br />\n零八年比你老師又中左一次，你有冇把握機會？<br />\n<br />\n信你咪好似你青城派個水晶姥姥咁賣左層樓買唔返囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪講緊陳雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嘅經濟觀點一向都唔同陳雲架喎，如果你有留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一向都係話樓價基於私樓供應，土地供應，同陳雲或者兩登主流講咩大陸人炒高個市唔同<br />\n<br />\n我一向都係講話香港樓價高唔關咩炒家事<br />\n<br />\n都唔知點解係要話我青城派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb517f3e0d258b8c49284438a8e758da92163aa","tid":339310,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我朋友06年買樓，啱啱供完層樓<br />\n宜家按左層樓去買元朗站上蓋，成五六百個</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}